        <ExplanationTxt>THE AMERICAN CIVIL LIBERTIES UNION OF ARKANSAS HAS MEMBERS. MEMBERS PAY A MINIMUM OF $35 PER YEAR IN SUPPORT OF THE ORGANIZATION EFFORTS. THE DUES ENTITLE MEMBERS TO BOTH STATE AND NATIONAL ACLU ORGANIZATIONS. MEMBERSHIP DUES ARE NOT TAX DEDUCTIBLE.</ExplanationTxt>
