        <FormAndLineReferenceDesc>Form 990, Part VI, Section A, Line 7a</FormAndLineReferenceDesc>
        <ExplanationTxt>THE ACLU MEMBERS HAVE THE RIGHT TO ANNUALLY ELECT THE BOARD OF DIRECTORS.</ExplanationTxt>
